{"tid":505533,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"乜都up wts gp又招人 無年齡限制禁錄音","createTime":"2017-12-21T08:24:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T02:14:39.000Z","uid":9178,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"53ec14b9eb23cc9c3c5b9b3dfd39420da9afffd7","tid":505533,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T08:24:04.000Z","msg":"放假悶又冇人陪可以搵我地睇下有無人陪你啦，純吹水都得 <br />\n<br />\n日日都好多野傾 返工返學生活事 有乜想傾岀聲就得 <br />\n<br />\n已搞過好多次聚會 除左飯聚 當然仲會有睇戲唱k行街個啲啦。夜場團飲下酒就唔少得㗎啦 <br />\n<br />\n歡迎隨時加入依個大家庭，外國嘅人都可以入黎吹水等回港搵我地玩，我地都有外國嘅巴絲打 <br />\n<br />\n潛水/發言量過少自知唔啱嘴型勿入<br />\n入到gp打5p字嘅更加咪入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上格劍gp嚟 搵食嘅可以慳返啖氣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/vw5aPdxyf49BKuc73\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2Fvw5aPdxyf49BKuc73&d=syBFdGYLvtjlZ21PBg1HBgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=3438ed23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/vw5aPdxyf49BKuc73</a>"},{"pid":"76144c08ad741347caf3564f1c6617f4976459a0","tid":505533,"uid":7903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T08:24:43.000Z","msg":"格劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"432a6edcff55ac257ae0bf2355c10a9012eff568","tid":505533,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T16:27:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14695d0ce9ca1a4d11efd38ed501f9230ca93780","tid":505533,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T04:4